OL,3,CBadenoch: Only Tories will stand up
OL,4,Cagainst SNP's 'divisive' referendum
OL,5,Cplans
OL,7,FOnly the Tories are prepared to "stand
OL,8,Fup" to SNP plans to hold another
OL,9,F"divisive" vote on independence, party
OL,10,Fleader Kemi Badenoch will say as she
OL,11,Fcampaigns in Scotland.
OL,13,FWith three weeks to go until voters
OL,14,Fcast their ballots in the Holyrood
OL,15,Felection, the UK Conservative leader
OL,16,Fis heading north to speak to
OL,17,Fsupporters at a rally in Edinburgh on
OL,18,FThursday.
OL,26,@oD@aOUpD@CO]qD@AOUqD@JO]
