PN,30404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1776301390
OL,3,CBadenoch: Only Tories will stand up
OL,4,Cagainst SNP's 'divisive' referendum
OL,5,Cplans
OL,7,FMrs Badenoch will tell supporters that
OL,8,Fthe Conservatives are "the only party
OL,9,Fprepared to stand up to this threat".
OL,11,FShe will also say that Reform UK `
OL,12,Fwhich some polls have suggested could
OL,13,Fbe the second largest party in
OL,14,FHolyrood after the May 7 election `
OL,15,F"don't give a monkey's about the
OL,16,FUnion".
OL,26,@pD@WOUqD@dO]wD@AOUxD@FO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/8
