PN,30405
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1776301390
OL,3,CBadenoch: Only Tories will stand up
OL,4,Cagainst SNP's 'divisive' referendum
OL,5,Cplans
OL,7,FHitting out at Nigel Farage's party,
OL,8,Fled in Scotland by Lord Malcolm
OL,9,FOfford, Mrs Badenoch will add: "They
OL,10,Fwill try and win at any cost, even if
OL,11,Fthat means diluting the Unionist vote
OL,12,Fand standing pro-independence
OL,13,Fcandidates.
OL,15,F"That's why I am calling on all pro-UK
OL,16,Fvoters to come together to stop an SNP
OL,17,Fmajority in this vital Holyrood
OL,18,Felection."
OL,26,@qD@`OUwD@AOUzD@JO]
