PN,30406
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1776301390
OL,3,CBadenoch: Only Tories will stand up
OL,4,Cagainst SNP's 'divisive' referendum
OL,5,Cplans
OL,7,FScottish Conservative leader Russell
OL,8,FFindlay hit out at Labour, whose UK
OL,9,Fleader Sir Keir Starmer has not
OL,10,Fvisited Scotland during the Holyrood
OL,11,Felection campaign, after Scottish
OL,12,FLabour chief Anas Sarwar called for
OL,13,Fthe Prime Minister to quit.
OL,15,FMr Findlay said: "I'm thrilled to be
OL,16,Fwelcoming Kemi Badenoch to the
OL,17,Fcampaign trail again. Unlike Anas
OL,18,FSarwar, our UK leader is an asset, not
OL,19,Fa liability."
OL,26,@wD@ROU{D@MO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
