FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30407
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1776301390
OL,3,CBadenoch: Only Tories will stand up
OL,4,Cagainst SNP's 'divisive' referendum
OL,5,Cplans
OL,7,FThe Scottish Tory leader added: "We
OL,8,Fsaw in the latest leaders' debate that
OL,9,FJohn Swinney is obsessed about pushing
OL,10,Ffor a divisive referendum if he wins
OL,11,Fthe election outright.
OL,13,F"That's why it's essential that pro-UK
OL,14,Fvoters back the Scottish Conservatives
OL,15,Fon their peach ballot to stop an SNP
OL,16,Fmajority and the constitutional chaos
OL,17,Fit would lead to."
OL,26,@oD@aOUuD@AOUyD@RO]
