CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1776301390
OL,3,CBadenoch: Only Tories will stand up
OL,4,Cagainst SNP's 'divisive' referendum
OL,5,Cplans
OL,7,FAn SNP spokesperson said: "The Tories
OL,8,Fhave absolutely nothing to offer the
OL,9,Fpeople of Scotland, but it is now no
OL,10,Fsecret that Anas Sarwar plans to rely
OL,11,Fon their votes ` and those of Reform `
OL,12,Fto force entry into Bute House.
OL,14,F"Only an SNP majority will lock out
OL,15,FFarage and unlock independence `
OL,16,Fthat's what's on the ballot on May 7
OL,17,Fand only a vote for John Swinney's
OL,18,Fstrong and experienced leadership can
OL,19,Fsecure that future."
OL,26,@oD@[OUvD@AOU{D@TO]
